Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:03.56,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.53,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,miushinatteshimaisou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.53,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
