Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:16.08,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain to me this happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.00,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,shiawase wa ittai nan desu ka{\b1\fscx98}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.00,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,that you just got to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.83,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,megumaresugeteite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.83,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you're so blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.66,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,omoidasenai kamo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.66,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can't even remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.55,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,ima koko ni iru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.55,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,That you stand here now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.38,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,iki wo shiteiru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.38,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,That you live and breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.43,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tada sore dake no koto ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.43,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all little miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.90,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,kiseki da to kizuku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.90,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,just by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.81,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,mijika ni arumono
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.81,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be extra careful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.94,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tsune ni ki wo tsuketeinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.94,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,with the things nearest to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:43.85,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,amari ni chikasugite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:43.85,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.52,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,miushinatteshimaisou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.52,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.90,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.53,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.12,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll never take it for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.91,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,oitsuzuketekita yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.91,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to say "Never give up."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.41,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,akiramezuni susume yo nante
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.41,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,and "Keep chasing your dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.16,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,kirei koto wo ieru hodo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.16,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,But the more time you spend talking big
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.84,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,nanimo dekichainai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.84,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the less you get done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.90,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,hitonigiri no yuuki wo mune ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.90,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll press that handful of courage against my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.72,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,ashita wo ikinuku tame ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.72,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,and with its help, survive another day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.64,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll never take it for granted
