Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:38.70,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HF0F0F0&\1a&H00&\bord0\fad(670,710)\pos(846,555)}Last Words
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just be another minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so powerless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can take us out with some gay little crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to hinder our view?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A black sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Shikamaru somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay on guard, Chouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but forget me, Captain Asuma is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's faint, but he still has a heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji, take Asuma-sensei to Konoha Hospital right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino, accompany him and use your medical ninjutsu to heal him as much as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up my bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll deal with them while you guys get Asuma-san out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can struggle all you like, but in the end you'll all be sacrificed to God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it wait a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, we're right at the best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to seal the Two-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That takes priority. Return immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! All I'm asking for is like another minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they communicating with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be right back, so make sure you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two really test my patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shithead leader... Next time I'm cursing {\i1}him{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they just going to pull back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino, Chouji, hurry up and get Asuma outta here! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We told you to stay here until we get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's about to die, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji, Ino, get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my healing ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I...can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three should realize it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got four vital organs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I finally understand why the Third did what he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, like always, I took too long...to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino, Chouji, Shikamaru... I have one last thing to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you shouldn't talk anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ino...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Asuma-sensei's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong willed, dependable and responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji and Shikamaru... They're total goof-offs. Keep them in line...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't let Sakura beat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in ninjutsu or romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji, you're a kind man who cares for his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...you'll become a shinobi more powerful than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more confident in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...maybe diet a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be too much, but I'll give it my best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so smart...and have great sense as a shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could definitely become Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...you're too lazy... You'd probably hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never even beat you once at shogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes... Remember our talk about the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we thought of the shinobi in Konoha as pieces of shogi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then, Shikamaru, you would probably be the Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then what about you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A sacrificial piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you know who the King is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it the Hokage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I used to think, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll know when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma! You...but-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter now, does it? Even though I quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in my pouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want one last smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry 'bout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sarutobi Asuma, and from today on I'll be leading Team 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not gonna be easy, so I hope you're all ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I did was say that I'm going to be strict!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your stupid smoke's making our eyes water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also bring out four more servings of Kalbi ribs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chouji-kun, have you ever heard of the word restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The bill's already 3,000 ryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like I'm trying to be stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you keep eating like this, eventually you're gonna get really f-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That word's taboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"F-" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something wrong, Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, h-h-h-h-he was saying you can order a full course meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really, Asuma-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks a million!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Waiter, bring two full course meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And pile on the rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boy, I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So who's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, uh... It's not really for anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}L-Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say hi to Kurenai-sensei for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-How'd she know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shogi? Too troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shogi allows you to work through various situations by utilizing each of the pieces' individual attributes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This game is a must for people like you who're good at coming up with strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should get a decent grasp on the rules if you read this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then you'll just need to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be troublesome, but I'll have it down in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You didn't have to hold back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the only one who passed the Chuunin Exams this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, as your supervising jounin, I'm very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now we need to get Chouji and Ino there. Keep working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Excellent work, Chouji, Ino!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since Shikamaru previously passed the exam, everyone in Team 10 is now a chuunin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that means I'm no longer in charge of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You three will go on to become captains and eventually lead your own teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These earrings are a present to celebrate your promotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't ever forget that the four of us were Team 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died the death of a true shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really hate cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke always makes...my eyes water.
